tile to describe your position relative to your classmates. For example, in item 1, If you think that your decision making abilities are below half of the class and above the other half of the class, enter \"50\" as your percentile. If you think that your decision making abilities are better than all the other students in this class, enter \"100.\"&nbsp; All numbers between \"0\" and \"100\" are acceptable responses.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span>","QuestionType":"DB","Selector":"TB","QuestionDescription":"For the following questions, please rate yourself in comparison to the other students in this cla...","Configuration":{"NumColumns":2,"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"Language":[],"QuestionText_Unsafe":"<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">For the following questions, please rate yourself in comparison to the other students in this class. For each item, please indicate (in the space provided) the percentile to describe your position relative to your classmates. For example, in item 1, If you think that your decision making abilities are below half of the class and above the other half of the class, enter \"50\" as your percentile. If you think that your decision making abilities are better than all the other students in this class, enter \"100.\"&nbsp; All numbers between \"0\" and \"100\" are acceptable responses.&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span>","DataExportTag":"Q1_BTA","QuestionID":"QID1218493889","DataVisibility":{"Private":false,"Hidden":false},"ChoiceOrder":[],"NextChoiceId":1,"NextAnswerId":1}},{"SurveyID":"SV_1H0RZtEDx1vZ7b8","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID1218493890","SecondaryAttribute":"Your decision making abilities","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"Your decision making abilities","QuestionType":"TE","Selector":"SL","QuestionDescription":"Your decision making abilities","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"ON","ForceResponseType":"ON","Type":"None"}},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"DataVisibility":{"Private":fal